@startuml
title Register & Verify Email - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Guest" as Guest
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "auth-service" as Auth
database "auth.users" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ\nuser.registered" as MQ
participant "mailer-service (Go)" as Mailer
participant "SMTP / Mailpit" as SMTP

Guest -> Web: Submit registration form
Web -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/auth/register
Gateway -> Auth: route request
Auth -> DB: validate uniqueness + insert user\nemailVerified=false
Auth -> MQ: publish UserRegisteredEvent
Auth --> Gateway: 201 Created / pending verification
Gateway --> Web: show verification notice
MQ -> Mailer: consume user.registered
Mailer -> SMTP: send verification email
SMTP --> Mailer: delivery accepted
Guest -> Web: Open verification link
Web -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/auth/verify-email
Gateway -> Auth: verify token
Auth -> DB: mark emailVerified=true
Auth --> Web: verification success
@enduml
